data.description: Amazing opportunity! Fantastic 3-bed, 2-bath mobile home with impressive mountain views on more than 1-acre corner lot! Natural desert front & back landscaping, a 2-car detached garage, and an extended front-covered patio for relaxing mornings or sunsets. Discover a large living room for entertaining, vaulted ceilings, laminate floors, and neutral paint to add your own taste. The ample eat-in kitchen offers a center island with breakfast bar, built-in appliances, wood cabinets, and a built-in desk. You'll love the split main retreat featuring an ensuite with dual sinks, a grab bar in the shower, and laundry access from the walk-in closet. The walk-in closets and plush carpeting add comfort to the bedrooms! Plenty of space for your horses or small animals to frolic in the field. Must see!
